here - any operating system, any language, using whatever compute is available. That gives an option to run code on the client, the server, and anywhere in between. Duration: 55 minutes.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-20T10:27:14.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"YuzheSHI/awesome-agi-cocosci","categoryHTML":"<h2>Academic Tools</h2><h3>Knowledge Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://luhmann.surge.sh/communicating-with-slip-boxes\">Communicating with Slip Boxes</a> - 2019. [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&#x26;as_sdt=0%2C5&#x26;q=Communicating+with+slip+boxes+luhmann&#x26;btnG=\">All Versions</a>].</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-20T08:29:39.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"brootware/awesome-cyber-security-university","categoryHTML":"<h2>Introduction and Pre-Security</h2><h3>Level 1 - Intro</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tryhackme.com/room/hipflask\">Hip Flask</a> - An in-depth walkthrough covering pentest methodology against a vulnerable server.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-20T07:42:00.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rockerBOO/awesome-neovim","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resource</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://neovimcraft.com\">Neovimcraft</a> - A site dedicated to searching for Neovim specific plugins and guides for building plugins in Lua.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-20T07:39:08.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jetli/awesome-yew","categoryHTML":"<h2>Official</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://play.yew.rs\">Playground</a> - Online playground for Yew.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-20T01:30:59.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaywcjlove/awesome-mac","categoryHTML":"<h2>Communication</h2><h4>Email Clients</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tutanota.com/\">Tutanota</a> - Encrypted email focused on security and privacy. <a href=\"https://github.com/tutao/tutanota\"><img src=\"https://jaywcjlove.github.io/sb/ico/min-oss.svg\" alt=\"Open-Source Software\" title=\"Open Source Software\"></a> <img src=\"https://jaywcjlove.github.io/sb/ico/min-free.svg\" alt=\"Freeware\